name: Zatanna
biography: A good stage magician and daughter of magician Giovanni John Zatara, Zatanna, the Mistress of Magic, after her father vanished, kidnapped by an old foe she delved into his library and learned about her ancestors, Zatanna taught herself how to get access to her power by speaking her spells backwards, and became one of most powerful magic-users in the DC Universe.

first_appearance.name: The Girl Who Split in Two!; The Machine that Magnetized Men!

creator: Gardner Fox
